<h2>oihana-php-standards</h2>
<p>A library of <strong>constants</strong>, <strong>value-objects</strong> and <strong>helpers</strong> built on top of international standards (ISO, IETF, UN/CEFACT, UN M49). Designed for <strong>strong typing</strong>, <strong>validation</strong> and <strong>easy lookups</strong> in your PHP 8.4+ applications.</p>

